  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0bae\u0bcd\u0bae\u0bbe\u0b9a\u0ba9\u0bae\u0bcd \u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 ? \u0b87\u0b9f\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb2 \u0b9c\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 4 \u0baa\u0bc7\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bcb\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Who has the throne? 4 candidates for Interim President",
      "author": "",
      "body_lines": [
        "According to the constitution, the next presidential election will take place through the parliament next week.",
        "While 4 main candidates have directly announced that they will contest for this, some others have also expressed their interest.",
        "In response, President Ranil Wickremesinghe, Opposition leader Sajith Premadasa, People's Liberation Front (JVP) leader Anurakumara Dissanayake, and Podujana Peramuna member Dalus Alagapperuma have announced that they will contest directly.",
        "Meanwhile, United People's Shakti General Secretary Field Marshal Sarath Fonseka and independent member Sampika Ranawaka have announced that they are ready to contest.",
        "Podujana Peramuna's general secretary, lawyer Sagara Kariyawasam, has announced that our party will vote for the alternate president, Ranil Wickremesinghe.",
        "However, the party's secretary, Professor G. L. Peiris, said, 'As our party member, we should vote for Dulles Alagapuruma.' mentioned that.",
        "Accordingly, the anti-Ranil parties in the Podujana Peramuna and those who are independent from the Podujana Peramuna are expected to vote for Dalas Alagaperuma.",
        "Laxman Kiriella, one of the senior vice-presidents of the United People's Shakti, had told a press conference yesterday that based on the votes obtained for Rohini Kaviratne, a Member of Parliament who contested on behalf of the opposition party during the recent vote for the election of the Deputy Speaker in Parliament, his candidate would get only 62 votes.",
        "How other candidates including Anurakumara Dissanayake will get votes or who will support them remains a question mark.",
        "But if Budujana Peramuna gives votes to both Ranil-Duls parties, the party's votes will be scattered. Also, if more than two candidates are contesting, 'preference vote' system will be used.",
        "Although political experts and activists have speculated that Ranil Wickremesinghe will be elected as the interim president, the increase in the number of candidates and the opportunity to vote has created huge expectations and doubts among everyone as to who will be the next president.",
        "'I am running for the presidency. I know Gotabaya Rajapaksa has the most dominant votes out of 225 MPs. It will be an uphill battle, but I am confident that truth will prevail.' It is also worth pointing out that Leader of the Opposition Sajith Premadasa has mentioned that."
      ],
